author: participant-20
message:
Insert TAF store directives and comment out bolus flux in horflux

- Since the adjoint code of horflux calculation in ecco_phys.F
  results in errors (taf_ad.log), add TAF store directives to
  avoid "extensive re-computations"
- Also re-organize code of horflux calculation to make it more
  compatible with TAF
- Comment out bolus addition to m_horflux_[theta/salt] because
  calling gmredi_x/ytransport.F still results in TAF errors
